[FILE:291:descriptions/desc.single]
This package contains xbrightness, a commandline tool for altering the
brightness (and optionally gamma) through the X server.

This version has been augmented by Akkana to brightness query and
bump up/bump down features.

See: http://shallowsky.com/blog/linux/brightness-contrast-in-x.html


